  <brief_title>Varenicline for Long-term Nicotine Replacement Therapy (NRT) Users</brief_title>
  <official_title>Varenicline for Long-term Nicotine Replacement Therapy (NRT) Users. A Double Blind, Placebo Controlled Trial</official_title>
