  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Long-term, daily NRT users (except nicotine patch) (&gt;11 months) ex-smokers that are
             willing to try to stop the use of NRT and adhere to this protocol.

          -  More than 4 pieces of nicotine gum/ sublingual tablets/ lozenges/ per day, OR more
             than 3 inhaler cylinders per day, OR

          -  more than 10 puffs of nasal spray per day.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 18 years,

          -  CO Smokers,

          -  Pregnant and lactating women,

          -  Used varenicline before,

          -  Not able to cooperate,

          -  Other significant diseases that might influence the trial (such as moderate -severe
             cardiac disease, lung cancer,) in expired air &gt; 7 ppm.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
